Connect HAT via usb
Connect usb-wlan-stick
Connect usb-keyboard
Connect hdmi
Connect ethernet

Login with usb-keyboard and hdmi

press enter

change password:

      $ passwd

set lan as dhcp to connect to local network
      $ uci set network.lan.proto=dhcp
      $ uci commit
      $ /etc/init.d/network restart

find ip:
      $ ifconfig
       => $IP
test connection: 
      $ ping google.com

test ssh connection from local terminal: 
      $ ssh root@$IP